## Example Categories

### Documentation Drift

#### docs-completeness
- description: Documentation should cover all features
- tolerance: All public APIs documented
- corrective: Update documentation
- severity: advisory

### Structural Drift

#### file-organization
- description: Files should follow project conventions
- tolerance: All files in correct directories
- corrective: Move files to correct locations
- severity: advisory

### Dependency Drift

#### dependency-versions
- description: Dependencies should be up-to-date
- tolerance: No outdated dependencies
- corrective: Run dependency update
- severity: advisory
